FBIS3-52387 "drnes002_s_94014" FBIS-NES-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 Iran Yazdi Criticizes Vatican Recognition of Israel LD0301170694 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 1630 GMT 3 Jan 94 LD0301170694 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Language: Persian Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Mr. Yazdi, head of the judiciary, spoke at today's meeting of the country's judiciary officials. While expressing surprise at the Vatican's stance in recognizing the usurping Zionist regime, he said: In international affairs it is necessary for the Vatican to uphold the religious views of the tradition of His Holiness Jesus Christ -- peace be upon Him -- and the views of His religious followers who are spread across the world, and it should not enter unjust political games that are tools of hegemonist powers against nations. [passage omitted]
